data.description: ***PRICE REDUCED** and ***NEW ROOF AT CLOSING with acceptable offer! - MOVE-IN READY!!! Welcome to this charming home, 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom with a convenient laundry room.  The kitchen includes brand new refrigerator, range and microwave, the great room feature new luxury vinyl plank flooring, adding a touch of elegance to the space. This home is located in the desirable High Springs Hills neighborhood and is ideally situated at walking distance from High Springs Community School, and close to the springs, grocery markets, shopping malls, restaurants, parks, downtown High Springs, just 25 minutes drive to Gainesville and easy access to I-75. Sitting on a spacious .25 acre lot, there is plenty of room to enjoy the beautiful backyard, as well as the front and back covered porches plus, there's no HOA, providing you with freedom and flexibility.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your new home!
